            "notes": "The deck focuses on utilizing mana dorks, ramp, and utility creatures to quickly generate mana and swarm the board with tokens. By utilizing cards like Elvish Mystic, Llanowar Elves, and Arbor Elf, the deck aims to generate massive amounts of mana to cast big threats like The Unbeatable Squirrel Girl and activate powerful abilities like Staff of Domination. Cards like Earthcraft and Cryptolith Rite allow for even more mana generation by tapping tokens for mana. The deck also includes ways to protect its creatures with cards like Sylvan Safekeeper and provide additional utility with cards like Survival of the Fittest. The overall strategy is to overwhelm the opponent with a massive board presence and aggressive attacks."
